metadata.description:
UNICORN WATCH is the ONLY podcast where tech-consumer veterans Mike Snickerberg and Don Moss download and demo today’s trendiest apps for your phone, watch, smart car or connected trousers.  Like seasoned pros at the racetrack, Mike and Don handicap the field of tech startups — helping YOU to pick an IPO winner in the next wave of irrational market exuberance.  Together, we’re making your world a better place for us and them!

www.unicorn.watch
